The paper discusses recent progress in NLP, specifically in the development of large-scale pre-trained language models based on Transformer. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the injection of semantic knowledge, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper conducts a thorough analysis of different model architectures and supervision configurations, which suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
